sequenceDiagram
    actor Player
    participant InputHandlerSystem
    participant Event Bus
    participant PlayerMovementSystem
    participant CollisionSystem
    participant PlayerEntity

    Player->>InputHandlerSystem: Provide Input [e.g., WASD keys]
    InputHandlerSystem->>Event Bus: InputEvent [Movement]
    Event Bus-->>PlayerMovementSystem: InputEvent [Movement]

    PlayerMovementSystem->>Event Bus: ProposeMovementEvent
    Event Bus-->>CollisionSystem: ProposeMovementEvent
    CollisionSystem-->>Event Bus: CollisionEvent [IF Collision Detected]
    Event Bus-->>PlayerMovementSystem: CollisionEvent [IF Collision Detected]
    PlayerMovementSystem->>PlayerEntity: UpdatePosition [IF No Collision]

